title: Manning shakes off interceptions, Broncos beat Browns 26-23
text:
> Sports Manning shakes off interceptions, Broncos beat Browns 26-23 Denver Broncos inside linebackers Brandon Marshall (54) and Danny Trevathan (59) celebrate after sacking Cleveland Browns quarterback Josh McCown during the first half of an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Cleveland. (AP Photo/David Richard)
